Emily Ratajkowski Walks Her Dog in Lingerie, as One Does 
Anything can happen in New York! By Sammy Nickalls Mar 13, 2017 The prime way to walk your dog, according to Emily Ratajkowski's latest DKNY campaign, is in almost nothing at all. In DKNY's newest campaign , Emily Ratajkowski wakes up in a cutesy New York apartment to walk her dog wearing nothing but boots and svelte black lingerie. The rest of the city reacts like anyone would: in pure shock and awe. Anything can happen in New York, yeahâ€”but something tells me this won't. Advertisement - Continue Reading Below "Finding inspiration in the confidence and attitude of a true New Yorker, our latest Intimates, Sleepwear, and Hosiery campaign features actress and model Emily Ratajkowski," the YouTube's description reads.
